descriptionHtml:
Are you preparing for IIT-JEE, NEET or any engineering or medical entrance exam or Olympiads, NTSE, CBSE, ICSE and state board exams? Or, do you aspire to pursue graduation from foreign universities?

Then Turito is the one-stop option for you! 👨‍🎓

Learn, practice and master to achieve success in IIT-JEE (Main + Advanced), NEET, state engineering and medical entrance exams along with NTSE, KVPY, Olympiads, CBSE, ICSE and other state board exams. Also, prepare for SAT and ACT to make your mark in your dream college/ university abroad.

Turito’s learning app brings together the best faculty, well-structured content, technology-enabled assessments and world-class learning experience for each and every student. Personalised learning approach and customised courses help students to learn at their convenience and pace.

With Turito, take live online classes, test series, doubt solving sessions, assessments, personal guidance and more from the comfort of your home!
Turito provides students online learning resources that help them learn, practice and master on-the-go. Through a perfect blend of technology and new-age teaching-learning practices, Turito has created an impactful learning journey for all types of learners.

-----------------------------------------

Try it yourself. Book a free demo class now!

------------------------------------------
We offer comprehensive preparation to build a strong foundation across Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics and Biology for classes 6-12, thereby preparing to ace IIT-JEE (Main + Advanced), NEET, other competitive exams and board exams. Our highly qualified and experienced faculties focus on every student’s overall success through personalised attention and differentiated teaching-learning practices.

How Turito creates a holistic learning journey?

💻 Interactive Live online classes by faculty members who have mentored toppers

👩‍🏫 SAT/ACT regular and weekend online courses and one-on-one online tutoring sessions

👨‍ High-quality recorded video lectures

📕 Well-structured study material- digital content and eBooks covering the entire syllabus of IIT-JEE, NEET, CBSE, ICSE and state boards for classes 6-10

📝 Exhaustive study material and digital content for SAT and ACT

👩🏿‍💻 Engaging and interactive on-demand videos spanning across all chapters and topics of Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics and Biology for classes 6-12

📝 Exhaustive practice and test series including Daily Practice Papers (DPPs), topic tests, chapter tests and full-length tests based on the actual exam pattern

📝 Previous years' solved papers for NEET & JEE, to enhance exam preparation

📝 IIT-JEE and NEET all-India test series for national-level performance evaluation

📊 Detailed performance analysis and reports

👉 Personalised learning path to improve student's learning experience

👩‍🏫 Dedicated guidance along with continuous academic support

💭 Regular doubt-clearing sessions

What’s more?

• Tips and tricks to solve lengthy questions

• Customised study plan and strategies to overcome areas of improvements

• Get real-time in-app notification for live classes, upcoming courses and recommendations curated just for you

• Attend the live classes or watch the recorded sessions, anytime from any of your device

• Get one-on-one mentoring by our experts

Choose Turito as your smart learning partner! Download the app now!

Whether you’re aiming to crack JEE, NEET, Olympiads, CBSE, ICSE, state boards, SAT or ACT, team Turito is committed to making sure that you achieve your goals.

And yes, the organisation continuously evolving to provide you an impactful learning experience and hence we be kept adding in the application.

What are you waiting for? Download the App and start your amazing learning journey. 🎓🏆
